	when exceptions are thrown, and some minor cleanups, bug-fixes

	* c++/ClTests.cc: Added inconsistent3() test, and run it.

	* c++/ClStrength.h: Added _pv memvar, and setPv(), Pv() -- needed
	for tracking ClStrengths in guile

